Thank You For the Favor

Last time I wanted to see how it would affect my download ranking at 
Amazon if readers downloaded some of my songs by clicking on the link: 
http://snipurl.com/eiu. 

Your response was tremendous. The ranking on many of the songs improved 
by 50 percent through most of the holidays. “Minstrel’s Song” had so 
many downloads that it was temporarily offline. You were a great help.

I won’t ask you to continue trying to boost the ranks. Thank you to each 
of you who tried it out. It was fun to watch.


